ash; Role). Because they\'re in [[*context+*plus cards]]:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{custom Related tabs}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Not copied to new Wagns, but here\'s where we design what gets turned into code for the config subtab of Related:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{config subtab|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<hr>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Process</h1>\n<ol>\n<li>Everything that can be done within cards is happening here. Just do things, and watch what each other are doing on Recent, and there\'s space for discussion at the bottom of this page.</li>\n<li>Everything that involves code is on [[http://wagn.org/wagn/implement_initial_setup_for_new_Wagn|the relevant ticket on wagn.org]] (everything there that was doable in cards has been done, or copied here).</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Todo</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Content / Wagneering<br></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>&radic;copy over remaining content from new.wagn</li>\n<li>Finish http://wagn.org/wagn/initial_permissions</li>\n<li>change many related tab cards\' names to star cards</li>\n<li>[[Cardtype+*tform]] (when pretty stable, copy/adapt to other [[cardtypes]])</li>\n<li>more +*edit on cardtypes?</li>\n<li>\n<p>[[*logo]] - make sure re licensing</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>Coding</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>test/design final on config tab</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Documentation<br></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Update http://wagn.org/wagn/star_cards</li>\n<li>[[http://wagn.org/wagn/configuration|configuration]] needs work to reflect changes.</li>\n<li>When documenting tickets that relate to [[http://wagn.org/wagn/Installation+tickets_for_item|installation]] or [[http://wagn.org/wagn/administration+tickets_for_item|administration]], make sure to update [[Config]].</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Discussion<br></h1>\n<hr>\n<p>[[*instances+*rform]] is in default, last-edited order. Sort alpha?</p>\n<p><em>&nbsp;&nbsp;--[[John Abbe]].....Mon Mar 02 08:10:02 -0800 2009</em></p>\n<hr>\n<p>I think i went ahead and did this. Thinking we might want