m|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Edit toolbar</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p><em>[[http://wagn.org/wagn/TinyMCE|How to customize the edit toolbar]].</em></p>\n<p>{{*tinyMCE|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Related tab</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p><em>[[*related|Some subtabs available are on every card]]:</em></p>\n<p>{{universal Related subtabs}}</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em>[[*related+*plus cards|Special type subtabs]] appear only on cards of a specific type:</em></p>\n<p>{{custom Related subtabs}}</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em>A special subtab appears on cards with accounts:</em></p>\n<p>{{*account+*rform|closed}}</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em>[[http://wagn.org/wagn/Related_tab|Learn more about the Related tab]].</em></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Google Analytics</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p><em>[[http://wagn.org/wagn/Google_Analytics|How to set up Google Analytics]]</em></p>\n<p>{{*google analytics key|type:Phrase}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><em></em></p>\n</blockquote>'),(2300,'2009-04-27 23:17:44',99,150,'{\"member_of\": \"_self\", \"sort\":\"name\"}'),(2303,'2009-04-27 23:19:55',192,150,''),(2304,'2009-04-27 23:19:56',193,150,'{\"found_by\": \"_self\", \"sort\": \"content\"}\n'),(2305,'2009-04-27 23:21:34',194,150,''),(2306,'2009-04-27 23:21:34',195,150,'{\"found_by\": \"_self\", \"dir\": \"desc\"}\n'),(2309,'2009-04-27 23:53:45',152,150,'<p><em><span>Cards and [[images]] in this Wagn are copied to new Wagns</span></em>. Exceptions should be added here:</p>\n<p>{{*ignore|closed}}</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>This one updates automatically:</p>\n<p>{{cards to copy to new Wagns|closed}}</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>What comprises those cards</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Account-related</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>[[*account]], [[WagnBot]], [[Anonymous]]</p>\n<p>{{Role+*type cards|closed}}</p>\n<p>[[*to]], [[*from]], [[*thanks]], [[Invite Success]], [[Signup Success]], [[Request Sent]]<br> {{*thanks+*plus cards|closed}}</p>\n</b