gn/initial_permissions&nbsp;</p>\n</li>\n<li>Add more [[Cardtype forms]]</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Documentation<br></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>[[http://wagn.org/wagn/configuration|configuration]] needs work to reflect changes.</li>\n<li>Write good docs on different signup options on wagn.org; link there and update here on [[Config]].</li>\n<li>Add +descriptions to more [[Cardtypes]]; [[Cardtype help text]]?</li>\n<li>When documenting tickets that relate to [[http://wagn.org/wagn/Installation+tickets_for_item|installation]] or [[http://wagn.org/wagn/administration+tickets_for_item|administration]], make sure to update [[Config]]. (make search to show ones from current/recent releases?)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Discussion</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),(2310,'2009-04-27 23:54:31',160,150,''),(2311,'2009-04-27 23:55:10',160,150,'<p>(DESIGN FOR CONFIG TAB)</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Formatting</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>((SHOWS UP if hard formatted by type)</p>\n<p><strong>By Type</strong></p>\n<p><em>Formats all ((type)) cards.&nbsp;</em> <em>[[http://wagn.org/wagn/formatting|Learn more about formatting]].</em></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{card\'s type+*tform|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>((SHOWS UP if simple or if hard formatted by name))</p>\n<p><strong>By Name<br></strong></p>\n<p><em>Formats any [[tag+plusses|plus card whose name ends in \"+((tagname)).\"]]&nbsp; [[http://wagn.org/wagn/formatting|Learn more about formatting]].</em></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{+*rform|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>((SHOWS UP on type or simple cards))</p>\n<h1>Help Text</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Editing Cards<br></strong></p>\n<p><em>Help text appears when </em><em>any ((if type -&gt;&nbsp; [type] cards, or ))</em><em> [[_left+plusses|plus card whose name ends in \"+((tag))\"]] is created or edited. [[http://wagn.org/wagn/help_text|Learn more about help text]].<br></em></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{+*edit|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>Creating Cards<br></strong></p>\n<p><em>