 in these +*rform cards, _left returns the name of the card on which one is viewing the Related tab.)</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Available on every card, because they\'re in [[*related]]:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{Related subtabs - universal|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Available on [[Cardtypes]] (under \"type\") because they\'re [[*related+*plus cards|plussed to *related]]:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{Related subtabs - cardtypes|closed}}</p>\n<p>[[*account+*rform]] - available on any card that has the account extension</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<hr>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Process</h1>\n<ol>\n<li>Everything about default Wagns that can be done within cards happens here. Make changes that make sense to you, and watch what each other are doing on Recent. There\'s space for discussion at the bottom of this page if you like.</li>\n<li>[[http://wagn.org/wagn/initial_permissions|Permissions are designed on wagn.org]] because people want to be able to choose different initial setups.</li>\n<li>Everything that involves code should be ticketed on wagn.org and perhaps listed below. Original development was described on [[http://wagn.org/wagn/implement_initial_setup_for_new_Wagn|implement initial setup for new Wagns]].</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Todo</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Content / Wagneering<br></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Copy/adapt [[Cardtype+*tform]] to more [[Cardtype forms]]; add more [[Cardtype descriptions]].</li>\n<li>make *ignore a Search that returns Users, Account Requests, and things referred to by *ignore+tag. (Requires changing the dump a little, but could bring new users in with less overhead.)</li>\n<li> Test and tweak http://wagn.org/wagn/initial_permissions (ongoing)</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Documentation<br></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>[[http://wagn.org/wagn/configuration|configuration]] needs work to reflect changes.</li>\n<li>When documenting tickets that relate to [[http://wagn.org/wagn/Installation+tickets_for_item|installation]] or [[http://wagn.org/wagn/administration+tickets_for_item|administration]], make sure to update [[Config]]. (make search to show ones from current/recent releases?)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Discussion</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),(2652,'2009-07-03 13:30:46',7,150,'<p>{{+description}}</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>[[/new/Role|Add a new role]]</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Roles</h1>\n<p>{{+*type cards}}</p>'),(2653,'2009-07-03 13:30:54',225,150,'<p>Each [[user]] has one or more roles, and each role\'s capabilities are defined in [[/admin/tasks|Global permissions]] (except for the [[Administrator]] role, which has all permissions). [[http://wagn.org/wagn/Role|Learn more about roles]].</p>'),(2657,'2009-07-06 17:38:24',63,149,'<p>People without an account can request one via a \"Sign Up\" link if you allow \"Anyone\" to [[/card/options/Account_Request|create account requests]].</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Unless [[*signup|approved automatically]], the <strong>request will be emailed to</strong>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{+*to|closed;type:Phrase}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>and the requester will be redirected here:</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span>HTTP:// <em>(YOUR WAGN\'S DOMAIN)</em></span><em> </em>{{+*thanks}}</p>'),(2665,'2009-07-10 15:56:00',198,150,'/* Body text */\nbody, .reset {\n  color: #444444;\n}\n\n/* Header text */\nh1, h2, body.wagn .card-slot h1, body.wagn .card-slot h2 {\n  color: #664444;\n}\nbody.wagn h1, body.wagn h2 {\n  color: #229; \n}\n\nbody.wagn {\n  background: url(/images/body-bg.png) repeat-x #CCC;\n}\n\n/* Main card and sidebar widths */\n#page-left {\n  width:67%;\n}\n#page-right {\n  width:28%;\n}\n\n/* Links: in-Wagn, to non-existent (wanted) cards, external, \"edited\" (on Recent Changes) */\na, a:link, a:visited {\n  color: #448844;\n}\n.card-slot a.wanted-card {\n  color: #990000;\n}\n.card-slot a.external-link,\n.card-slot.line .content a.external-link,\n.card-slot a.email-link {\n  color: #997799;\n}\n.card-slo