</h2>\n<p>(Note that in these +*rform cards, _left returns the name of the card on which one is viewing the Related tab.)</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Available on every card, because they\'re in [[*related]]:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{Related subtabs - universal|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Available on [[Cardtypes]] (under \"type\") because they\'re [[*related+*plus cards|plussed to *related]]:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{Related subtabs - cardtypes|closed}}</p>\n<p>[[*account+*right+*content]] - available on any card that has the account extension</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<hr>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Process</h1>\n<ol>\n<li>Everything about default Wagns that can be done within cards happens here. Make changes that make sense to you, and watch what each other are doing on Recent. There\'s space for discussion at the bottom of this page if you like.</li>\n<li>If you remove stuff from [[Config]] that may still be relevant later, add it to http://www.wagn.org/wagn/English_Wagn+not_ready </li>\n<li>For changes/additions here to show up in already-existing Wagns, put a note in the next [[http://www.wagn.org/wagn/Release|Wagn release]]\'s discussion about which cards you want migrated.</li>\n<li>[[http://wagn.org/wagn/initial_permissions|Permissions are specified on wagn.org]], because we want people to be able to choose different initial setups.</li>\n<li>Everything that involves code should be ticketed on wagn.org.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Todo</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Content / Wagneering<br></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>make *ignore a Search that returns Users, Account Requests, and things referred to by *ignore+tag. (Requires changing the dump a little, but could bring new users in with less overhead.)&nbsp; <em>eventually.&nbsp;&nbsp; not ready for this yet --efm</em></li>\n<li> Test and tweak http://wagn.org/wagn/initial_permissions (ongoing)</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Documentation<br></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>When documenting tickets that relate to [[http://