p>{{*all|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><em></em></p>\n</blockquote>'),(5345,'2011-02-27 18:52:45',56,150,'<p><em>Any user who is signed in and has the [[/admin/tasks|global permission]] to \"create accounts\" can invite new users via email.</em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Email subject</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{+*subject|type:Phrase}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Email message</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{+*message|type:PlainText}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Email from</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{+*from|type:Phrase}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>After sending an invitation, you\'re taken here:</strong><span><strong></strong></span></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>HTTP:// <em>(YOUR WAGN\'S DOMAIN) </em>{{+*thanks}}</p>\n</blockquote>'),(5347,'2011-02-27 18:53:29',56,150,'<p><em>Any user who is signed in and has the [[/admin/tasks|global permission]] to \"create accounts\" can invite new users via email.</em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Email subject</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{+*subject|type:Phrase}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Email message</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{+*message|type:PlainText}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Email from</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{+*from|type:Phrase}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>After sending an invitation, you\'re taken here:</strong><span><strong></strong></span></p>\n<blockquote>\n<div>HTTP:// <em>(YOUR WAGN\'S DOMAIN) </em>{{+*thanks}}</div>\n</blockquote>'),(5350,'2011-02-27 18:54:43',56,150,'<p><em>Any user who is signed in to this Wagn and has the [[/admin/tasks|global permission]] to \"create accounts\" can invite new users via email.</em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Email subject</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{+*subject|type:Phrase}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Email message</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{+*message|type:PlainText}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Email from</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{+*from|type:Phrase}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>A