p>\n<p>[[by update+*right+*content]]</p>\n<p>[[by create+*right+*content]]</p>\n<hr>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Process</h1>\n<ol>\n<li>Everything about default Wagns that can be done within cards (except permissions, see below) happens here. Make changes that make sense to you, and watch what each other are doing on Recent. There\'s space for discussion at the bottom of this page if you like.</li>\n<li>To <strong>migrate</strong> cards you add or change here to existing Wagns, put  a note in the [[http://wagn.org/Next_Wagn_Release|next Wagn release\'s]]  discussion about which cards you want migrated.</li>\n<li>Cards that are <strong> deleted</strong> should also be noted as migrations if it would cause a problem to leave them in. Otherwise, add them to the list at  http://www.wagn.org/wagn/migrations+to_delete (we only migrate deletions once in a  while).</li>\n<li>Default [[http://wagn.org/wagn/initial_permissions|<strong>permissions</strong> are  specified on wagn.org]], because we want people to be able to choose among several different initial setups.</li>\n<li><strong>Document</strong> changes and additions at http://wagn.org/Default_cards and http://wagn.org/star_cards</li>\n<li>Things you remove from [[Config]] that may be relevant later can be added to http://www.wagn.org/wagn/en+not_ready</li>\n<li>Anything that involves code should be [[http://wagn.org/new/Ticket|ticketed]] on wagn.org.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Todo</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Content / Wagneering<br></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Adapt or include [[default cards]] for the \"What comprises...\" section above.</li>\n<li>Test and tweak http://wagn.org/wagn/initial_permissions (ongoing)</li>\n<li>make *ignore a Search that returns Users, Account Requests, and things referred to by *ignore+tag. (Requires changing the dump a little, but could bring new users in with less overhead.)&nbsp; <em>eventually.&nbsp;&nbsp; not ready for this yet --efm</em></li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Documentation<br></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>When documenting tickets that relate to [[http://wagn.org/wagn/Installation+tickets_for_item|installation]] or [[http://wagn.org/wagn/administration+tickets_for_item|administration]], make sure to update [[Config]]. (make search to show ones from current/recent releases?)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Discussion</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),(5767,'2011-07-19 11:17:37',154,149,'[[Ethan McCutchen]]\n[[John Abbe]]\n[[Lewis Hoffman]]\n[[*ignore]]\n[[cards to copy to new Wagns]]\n[[new]]\n[[all non-star cards]]\n[[cards by type]]\n[[Cardtype descriptions]]\n[[Basic+*watchers]]\n[[related subtabs - universal]]\n[[Rules]]\n[[not set or setting]]\n[[translatable cards]]\n[[default cards]]\n[[star cards]]\n[[not listed yet]]\n[[Settings defaults and help]]\n[[Advanced Search]]\n[[new+*self]]\n[[new+*self+*comment]]'),(5768,'2011-07-19 11:48:54',524,149,'{\"right\":\"_self\"}'),(5769,'2011-07-19 11:48:54',525,149,'<p>Who can comment on cards in set.</p>'),(5770,'2011-07-19 11:49:18',526,149,'{\"right\":\"_self\"}'),(5771,'2011-07-19 11:49:18',527,149,'<p>Who can create cards in the set.</p>'),(5772,'2011-07-19 11:49:45',528,149,'{\"right\":\"_self\"}'),(5773,'2011-07-19 11:49:45',529,149,'<p>Who can remove cards in the set.</p>'),(5774,'2011-07-19 11:49:58',527,149,'<p>Who can add cards in the set.</p>'),(5775,'2011-07-19 11:50:19',530,149,'{\"right\":\"_self\"}'),(5776,'2011-07-19 11:50:19',531,149,'<p>Who can view cards in the set.</p>'),(5777,'2011-07-19 11:50:35',532,149,'{\"right\":\"_self\"}'),(5778,'2011-07-19 11:50:35',533,149,'<p>Who can edit cards in the set.</p>'),(5779,'2011-07-19 18:08:56',534,149,''),(5780,'2011-07-19 18:10:30',535,149,'{\"extension_type\":\"User\"}'),(5781,'2011-07-19 18:22:11',536,149,''),(5782,'2011-07-19 18:24:02',537,149,'{\"extension_type\":\"User\"}'),(5783,'2011-07-19 18:24:14',535,149,'{\"extension_type\":\"User\"}'),(5784,'2011-07-19 18:24:54',538,149,'{\"extension_type\":\"User\"}'),(5785,'2011-07-19 18:25:03',538,149,'